summary: swab samples were collected from healthy dogs (n = 55) and dogs with gastroenteritis symptoms (n = 252) of 307 swab samples tested by one-step RT-PCR specific to 3D gene, we found CaKoV positivity at 17.59% (54/307). the virus is frequently detected in younger dogs. gonucleotide primers used for whole genome sequencing. gonucleotide primers used for CaKoV whole genome sequencing.
